Package service

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClearService
    The ClearService class clears all data from the database
    EventIDService
    The EventIDService class gets the event that matches the given event ID
    EventService
    The EventService class gets all of the events of the given user
    FillService
    The FillService class generates Persons and Events for a given user name
    LoadService
    Clears the database and loads arrays of Users, Persons, and Events
    LoginService
    The LoginService class logs a user in
    PersonIDService
    The PersonIDService gets the Person that matches the given personID
    PersonService
    The PersonService class gets all Persons for the given user
    RegisterService
    The RegisterService class adds new users to the database and generates family history data
